- Mm-hmm.
- Identical?

40:29.469 --> 40:30.678
- Identical.
- Oh.

40:30.678 --> 40:32.555
I know.

40:32.555 --> 40:36.309
<i>♪ But as long as we keep ♪
every promise ♪</i>

40:36.309 --> 40:37.435
<i>Meredith:
Often we can't even be sure</i>

40:37.435 --> 40:39.228
<i>if our time has passed...</i>

40:39.228 --> 40:40.897
<i>♪ ♪</i>

