<i>♪ I know ♪</i>

40:44.776 --> 40:46.069
<i>♪ There'll be heavy days ♪</i>

40:46.069 --> 40:48.154
- Is Yasuda home?
- Joe's.

40:48.154 --> 40:51.532
- To eat, not work.
- Huh.

40:51.532 --> 40:54.619
- I'm so sorry about Ray.
- Yeah, yeah, me too.

40:54.619 --> 40:56.955
<i>♪ ♪</i>

40:56.955 --> 40:58.373
- So...
- Oh, you can...

40:58.373 --> 40:59.916
You can--you can have one.

40:59.916 --> 41:02.126
There is plenty.

41:02.126 --> 41:04.754
<i>♪ Sweet symphony ♪</i>

