but there's this thing,
this symptom

41:13.388 --> 41:17.308
where you get stuck
in your head, you overthink,

41:17.308 --> 41:20.144
you have a hard time
saying what you mean,

41:20.144 --> 41:21.729
because you can't help
but think about

41:21.729 --> 41:26.693
all the possible ramifications,
and so...

41:26.693 --> 41:29.112
<i>♪ ♪</i>

41:29.112 --> 41:32.615
- Don't get married.
- Lucas.

41:32.615 --> 41:37.578
Maybe--maybe I'm too late,
or maybe I lost my chance.

41:37.578 --> 41:39.831
But I wouldn't be able
to live with myself

41:39.831 --> 41:43.167
if I didn't tell you
while you still had time

41:43.167 --> 41:45.962
to change your mind.

41:45.962 --> 41:47.422
Trey doesn't see you,

41:47.422 --> 41:51.300
or maybe he sees
an old version of you,

41:51.300 --> 41:53.344
but I see you.

41:53.344 --> 41:56.222
Simone, I see you...

41:56.222 --> 42:01.477
and I love
every single thing I see.

42:01.477 --> 42:03.688
<i>♪ Even if the world ♪</i>

42:03.688 --> 42:07.525
<i>♪ That we built
falls at our feet ♪</i>

42:07.525 --> 42:11.362
<i>♪ We're still right where
we're supposed to be ♪</i>

42:11.362 --> 42:13.823
<i>♪ Together through ups
and the downs ♪</i>

42:13.823 --> 42:15.616
<i>Meredith: And all we can do
is seize the present.</i>

